  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2914046/" class="title-link">意识的宇宙</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2914046"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/miao126/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4806921-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/miao126/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">qhors苗广飞</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-05 13:59:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2914046_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  头脑就是意识的宇宙，因此就是意识的产生和幻觉的产生的来源。但是头脑是置身意识世外的。没有了这些头脑可以继续存在，但是意识却并不能脱离头脑而独立存在，因此意识不仅不应该反对头脑，还应该维护头脑的正常功能，否则就不能够存在，或者不应该存在。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2914046/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2914046_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2914046_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
